MORE OF THE SCORE - OCT. 10 
By DONOVAN KLEIN October 10, 2015 Updated Oct 10, 2015 at 12:32 AM EDT 
FORT WAYNE, IND. (21ALIVE) - In the Oct. 9 episode of More of the Score 21Alive's Kent Hormann and President and CEO of AWP, Michael Ledo talk about the big match up this week between Dwenger and Snider. The guys also check in on some of the other big match-ups in the area as the High School football season remains in full swing.   To submit a comment on this article, your email address is required.
